As the successor of HerobrineUnleashed and BasicHerobrine, this plugin brings back the legend, the torcher, the hell... 
him. Developed by Nicholas Krecklow, it is a complete rewrite of Herobrine and sets the legend right.

Various links and information that can help if you have any problems, comments, questions, or concerns...
